547c97d93377fb1c4a31bc1e8032b44466421be1","tid":746503,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T00:06:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主同事主前世撈亂骨頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f2b4108e459a9c6c07fc4d6819e3a8b8028616","tid":746503,"uid":161050,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:05:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">祺　感化還好嗎　尚愛拍少女裸體嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近　近乎沒露面　你有新對象嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n＊真想你帶我見　你剛識到的她<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n　我想聽你意見　這算是病吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n　為何無論你　願意怎樣試<br />\n　怎樣也不可抗拒去偷拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>(怎樣也沒令自己戀上她)<br />\n<br />\n＃難道沒練習太耐　感覺都追不回來<br />\n　試圖再努力愛　也顯得不自在<br />\n　不懂得如何談戀愛　還是我太愛你　對過去太放不開<br />\n<br />\n△難道是寂寞太耐　生鏽的鎖不能開<br />\n　鑰匙也拆斷了　留在舊患所在<br />\n　懷內　放滿對你的愛　難怪跟誰也　再沒法戀愛<br />\n<br />\n我　有時仍很怕　路過你那從前的家<br />\n往事若然未落幕　再揭起有害嗎<br />\n<br />\nRepeat (＊),＃,△<br />\n<br />\n難道沒練習太耐　感覺都追不回來<br />\n試圖再努力愛　也顯得不自在<br />\n耿耿於懷從前的愛　從沒有振作過　痛了再痛也應該<br />\n<br />\n難道是寂寞太耐　生鏽的鎖不能開<br />\n往事卻似斷箭　還剩下在體內<br />\n若懷內　放滿對你的愛　害怕一直也　再沒法戀愛"},{"pid":"e6992d8d744556fe5bc769621bdec9f5c30730b0","tid":746503,"uid":161050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">祺　感化還好嗎　尚愛拍少女裸體嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"h